    <title>自動部屬設定</title>
    <url>/second.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="自動部屬設定"><a href="#自動部屬設定" class="headerlink" title="自動部屬設定"></a>自動部屬設定</h1><p>可參考<br><a href="https://hadronw.com/2018/05-27/travis-autodeploy-github-with-coding/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hadronw.com/2018/05-27/travis-autodeploy-github-with-coding/</a><br>因有改theme<br>所以要加一段在</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">before_install:</span><br><span class="line">    - export TZ=&apos;Asia/Taipei&apos; # 更改时区</span><br><span class="line">    - npm install hexo-cli -g  # 安装hexo环境</span><br><span class="line">    - git clone https://github.com/chianChen/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br><span class="line">    - chmod +x ./publish-to-gh-pages.sh  # 为shell文件添加可执行权限</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>記得要先去 Fork 原來 theme</p>
<h1 id="標籤與分類"><a href="#標籤與分類" class="headerlink" title="標籤與分類"></a>標籤與分類</h1><p>因為我最後都是在github上直接修改檔案</p>
<p>所以我是直接在</p>
<p>我的 hexo 分支內的 source</p>
<p>分別建立 categories 與 tags 檔案夾</p>
<p>再到裡面建 index.md</p>
<p>內容分別是</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">文章分类</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2019</span><span class="bullet">-05</span><span class="bullet">-08</span> <span class="number">00</span><span class="string">:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"categories"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>與</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">文章標籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2019</span><span class="bullet">-05</span><span class="bullet">-08</span> <span class="number">00</span><span class="string">:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"tags"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>儲存後再到 Fork 出的主題包 hexo-theme-next 裡面修改</p>
<p>_config.yml</p>
<p>把這兩個</p>
<p>tags: /tags/ || tags<br>categories: /categories/ || th</p>
<p>前面的 # 拿掉</p>
<p>再去執行一次 travis 裡面的 Restart build 就成功囉</p>
]]></content>
